'''1987''', real name '''Victor Holmberg''' (born 28 April 1987), is a producer, songwriter and musician of solo projects. He is also a member of the Swedish [[electronic music]] duo '''Montauk'''.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lagasta.com/montauk-the-newsroom-ep/ |title=Montauk: "The Newsroom" EP |work=[[Last Gas Station]] |date=30 March 2013 |accessdate=8 December 2013}}</ref>
==History== In September 2013, '''1987''' released his debut single, "Ocean".<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefader.com/2013/09/16/1987-ocean-swedish-pop-music/ |title=Stream 1987, "Ocean" |work=[[The Fader]] |date=16 September 2013 |accessdate=8 December 2013}}</ref>
